---
title: Szechuan Chicken Stir-Fry with Chicken Thighs, Ginger Rice & Candied Peanuts
description: Put down that delivery menu! This sweet-savory-spicy stir-fry (say that 5 times fast) has got you covered. You’ll toss tender dark-meat chicken and green beans in an addictive Szechuan sauce that’s got just the right touch of heat. Everything’s served over steamy, ginger-infused rice, then topped with crunchy candied peanuts. Plus, it’s all ready in just 30 minutes—take that, takeout!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/szechuan-stir-fry-with-chicken-thighs-d592f653.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/szechuan-chicken-stir-fry-645ba2a67364490af90dd7e6-01a2ca50.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Chinese
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/szechuan-chicken-stir-fry-645ba2a67364490af90dd7e6
nutrition:
  calories: 770 kcal
  fat: 24 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 101 g
  sugar: 23 g
  protein: 40 g
  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 1680 mg
servings: 2
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
